    "body": "## Notes:\r\n- Since version 26.2+, Mojang has introduced the Vulkan rendering engine. If your device does **not** support **Vulkan 1.2**, please do **not** use the **Vulkan backend** to launch the latest version of Minecraft.\r\n\r\n## Refactors:\r\n- [GP#1367](https://github.com/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/pull/1367): Rewrote control layout interaction logic (by @MovTery)\r\n\r\n## Changes:\r\n- [GP#1358](https://github.com/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/pull/1358): Search ID input field now supports pressing Enter to search (by @MovTery)\r\n- [GP#1359](https://github.com/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/pull/1359): Updated project dependencies (by @MovTery)\r\n- [GP#1369](https://github.com/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/pull/1369): Theme: Use Scheme's built-in Surface color attributes (by @MovTery)\r\n\r\n## Fixes:\r\n- [GP#1357](https://github.com/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/pull/1357): Physical mouse movement position and stylus event handling (by @MovTery)\r\n- [Main#8c4f2c6](https://github.com/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/commit/8c4f2c6): Game manifest merge logic should use the original assetsIndex (by @MovTery)\r\n- [Main#8c4f2c6](https://github.com/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/commit/8c4f2c6): Clean game files should ignore non-existent version JSONs (by @MovTery)\r\n- [GP#1366](https://github.com/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/pull/1366): Pass current account data via Intent during launch process (by @MovTery)\r\n- [GP#1368](https://github.com/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/pull/1368): Attempting to render blur effect when no background is set (by @MovTery)",
